---
import MyPhoto from "../../assets/img/profile.jpg";
---
<!-- Main Container -->
<div
  class="mx-auto mt-20 flex max-w-6xl flex-col items-center gap-8 px-6 lg:flex-row"
>
  <!-- Image -->
  <div
    class="border-primary h-64 w-64 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-lg md:h-96 md:w-96 drop-shadow-[4px_4px_0_#7836cf]"
  >
    <img
      src={MyPhoto.src}
      alt="Photo of Daniel"
      class="h-full w-full object-cover"
    />
  </div>
  <!-- Text -->
  <div class="flex-1 text-center text-gray-300 lg:text-left">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">
      My name is <span class="text-white text-shadow">Daniel Aunan</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4">
      I'm a cybersecurity engineer with a strong foundation in 
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">network operations</span> and 
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">infrastructure security</span>. 
      Currently working as an OT Network Technician at Intility in Oslo, I focus on 
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">operational technology platforms</span>, 
      network monitoring, and ensuring the resilience of critical infrastructure. 
      My solid networking knowledge is backed by 
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">CCNA certification</span> and hands-on experience 
      in both IT and OT environments.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2">
      My international journey has taken me across Europe and Asia. I earned a 
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">double master's degree</span> â€” 
      in Computer & Network Engineering from <span class="text-primary font-semibold">INSA Toulouse, France</span> 
      and in Security of Computer Systems from <span class="text-primary font-semibold">ENSEEIHT (TLS-SEC)</span>. 
      During my studies, I completed an exchange semester at 
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">Seoul National University of Science and Technology in South Korea</span>, 
      broadening my technical and cultural perspectives. I then worked in 
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">Brussels, Belgium</span> at EUROCONTROL's EATM-CERT, 
      conducting penetration testing and developing CTF challenges for the European aviation community.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2">
      This diverse international experience has shaped my ability to 
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">adapt quickly</span> to new environments, technologies, and teams. 
      Whether it's learning new security frameworks, mastering emerging network technologies, or collaborating 
      across cultures, I thrive on <span class="text-primary font-semibold">continuous learning</span> and 
      staying ahead of the evolving landscape in <span class="text-primary font-semibold">cybersecurity</span> 
      and <span class="text-primary font-semibold">network operations</span>.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>